Description: Professional archive manager for VAXP-OS
 VArchive is a full-featured File Roller alternative matching the VAXP-OS
 glassmorphism design language. It natively supports creating, extracting,
 and modifying over 40 archive formats including ZIP, TAR.GZ, 7Z, RAR, and ISO.
